---
---

<section class="bg-white py-20 lg:py-24">
  <div class="section-container">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="max-w-2xl mb-14">
      <p class="text-periwinkle font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Who We Help</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading mb-4">Safe housing for those who need it most</h2>
      <p class="text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed">
        We work with the people in our communities who face the greatest barriers to finding safe, stable housing.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Cards -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-8">

      <!-- Card 1: Leave to remain -->
      <div class="bg-periwinkle-light rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-10">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-periwinkle/15 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-7 h-7 text-periwinkle" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-3" style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">
          People Granted Leave to Remain
        </h3>
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
          When someone is granted leave to remain in the UK, they have an immediate problem: finding housing fast, often with limited English, no UK rental history, and little familiarity with the benefits system. We work specifically with this group, matching them with housing providers who know their situation and have rooms in supported accommodation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Other vulnerable individuals -->
      <div class="bg-warm-cream rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-10">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-charcoal/5 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-7 h-7 text-charcoal" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-3" style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">
          Other Vulnerable Individuals
        </h3>
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
          We also support others who need stable housing, whether they are at risk of homelessness or going through a housing crisis. We work with charities, social workers, and local authority teams to make sure nobody is left without somewhere to turn.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom note -->
    <div class="mt-10 flex items-start gap-3 p-5 bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl max-w-2xl">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-periwinkle flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
      </svg>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
        <strong class="text-charcoal">The individual never pays.</strong> Our referral service is entirely free to the person being housed. We are funded through referral fees paid by housing providers.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
